Simulated data sets for different types of outliers

Source: R/data-outliers.R
outliers.Rd

Data sets for showing different types of outliers

outliers

Format

A tibble with 50 observations on the following 5 variables.

x

a numeric vector

y

a numeric vector

x_inf

a numeric vector

y_lev

a numeric vector

y_out

a numeric vector

Examples


outliers
#> # A tibble: 50 x 5
#>        x      y x_inf  y_lev  y_out
#>    <int>  <dbl> <int>  <dbl>  <dbl>
#>  1     1   6.18     1   6.18   6.18
#>  2     2  16.0      2  16.0   16.0 
#>  3     3  12.4      3  12.4   12.4

#>  5     5  24.9      5  24.9   24.9

#>  7     7  24.7      7  24.7   24.7 
#>  8     8 -10.2      8 -10.2  -10.2 
#>  9     9  -2.92     9  -2.92  -2.92
